3u8&quot;},&quot;userId&quot;:0,&quot;premium&quot;:false,&quot;datePublished&quot;:1724439960,&quot;videoAdPartner&quot;:&quot;desktop%2Fgamespot.com&quot;,&quot;videoAdMobilePartner&quot;:&quot;mobile_web%2Fgamespot.com_mobile&quot;}" data-non-iframe-embed="1" data-jw-context-name="gamespot" data-jw-media-id="aUN4pVVG" data-jw-player-url="https://cdn.jwplayer.com/libraries/VXc5h4Tf.js" data-jw-video-token="" data-has-youtube="" data-youtube-icon-path="https://www.gamespot.com/a/bundles/phoenixsite/images/core/loose/icn-youtube-30x30.png" id="video-rectangle" data-embed-type="video" data-ref-id="2300-6464966" data-src="/videos/avowed-refreshes-the-fantasy-action-genre-gamespot-preview-gamescom-2024/2300-6464966/" data-width="100%" data-height="100%" data-video-start="0"><div><p>Avowed Refreshes The Fantasy Action Genre | GameSpot Preview | gamescom 2024</p><div><p>         Want us to remember this setting for all your devices?       </p><p><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/signup/">Sign up</a> or <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/login/">Sign in</a> now!       </p></div></div><p>       Please use a html5 video capable browser to watch videos.     </p><p>       This video has an invalid file format.     </p><p>Sorry, but you can't access this content!</p></div><p dir="ltr">As such, Spencer worked with Xbox Game Studios head Matt Booty on scheduling out game releases and working with the Game Pass team. "We said, 'OK, let's make sure we pace this out a little better.'”</p><p dir="ltr">Avowed is now slated to launch on PC and Xbox Series X|S on February 18, 2025. <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/2025-upcoming-games-release-schedule/1100-6526471/" data-ref-id="1100-6526471">It's not a barren month</a> by any means, as other big games scheduled then include Civilization VII and Monster Hunter Wilds.</p><p dir="ltr">Earlier this year, Obsidian revealed that <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/avowed-will-be-30fps-on-xbox-series-x-allowing-for-juicier-visual-effects/1100-6526077/" data-ref-id="1100-6526077">Avowed will run at 30fps on Xbox Series X</a>, enabling "juicier visuals." The developer is promising <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/avowed-possible-endings-number-in-the-double-digits/1100-6526049/" data-ref-id="1100-6526049">possible endings in Avowed that "number in the double digits."</a> GameSpot got an hour with the RPG in August, coming away with the impression that <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/xbox-exclusive-avowed-is-like-skyrim-plus-one-of-the-last-decades-best-sci-fi-movies/1100-6526088/" data-ref-id="1100-6526088">Avowed is like Skyrim mixed with Annihilation</a>.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
